Connected on 19-of-25 FG attempts in '08 with a long of 49 and made 29-of-30 PATs while punting 59-41.4-L61-23. Was successful on 8-of-13 FG attempts with a long of 29 and made 19-of-20 PATs. Missed four games as he nursed a hip flexor injury. In '10, made 17-of-24 FG attempts with a long of 52 and 42-of-45 PATs. Also handled kickoffs 75-64.2-12 and punted 6-36.2-L49-0. Team captain.
